   A number of American actors are here as directors: Matt Dillon
with "City of Ghosts," about a con artist who wants to go straight;
Robert Duvall, who mixes tango and skulduggery in "Operation Tango";
and Denzel Washington with "The Antwone Fisher Story," based on
memoirs of abuse.

DOC.LD:
The captain of an aircraft carrier stationed in Japan was removed
from command due to "a loss of confidence" in his ability to lead,
the U.S. Navy said Tuesday.
